Provides a configuration for the ssh daemon

@author Gunnar Wrobel <p@rdus.de>
@version 1.0
@package service_openssh

@module os_gentoo     The os_gentoo module is required for Gentoo support.

@fact operatingsystem Allows to choose the correct actions depending
                      on the operating system

@param allow_root     Allow root login via SSH.
                      (Default: true)
@param allow_root     Allow password based login via SSH.
                      (Default: false)
@param allow_x11      Allow X11 forwarding via SSH.
                      (Default: false)
@param run_services   Determines if the cron service should be started.
                      (Default: true)
